<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1054.67554.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Fish species from the middle-southern Espinhaco mountain range, Minas Gerais state, Brazil A Gymnotiformes (Gymnotus carapo group, MNRJ 48407, 130.5 mm SL) B Synbranchiformes (Synbranchus marmoratus group, MNRJ 48448, 116.8 mm SL) C Cyprinodontiformes (Phalloceros uai, MNRJ 48408, 32.0 mm (female - above) and 16.3 mm (male - below) SL) D Cichliformes (Australoheros mattosi, MNRJ 48454, 54.6 mm SL E Cichliformes (Australoheros sp., MNRJ 46859, 39.3 mm SL)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/573398" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

